import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-user-list-data', templateUrl: './user-list-data.component.html', }) export class UserListDataComponent { public users: User[] = []; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get(baseUrl + 'userlist').subscribe(result => { this.users = result; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface User { username: string; email: string; password: string; }
